<br>
I want to go group in KC, but not if it will hurt relations with the OT dwellers. Evils have to keep as many friends as possible! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
